title: Barr letter
added: In his own statement, House Minority Leader [[Kevin McCarthy (California politician)|Kevin McCarthy]] declared, based on the conclusions in the Barr Letter and the vast scope and resources made available to Mueller, that "This case is closed." McCarthy emphasized the need to move on from the investigation "after months upon months of manufactured outrage."
